    "faq": {
      "type": "faq",
      "blocks": {
        "question-1": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<strong>Riding Range Test | Brawn</strong>",
            "text": "<p>Max Range: 45 miles(pure electric) / 65 miles(pedal assist )</p><p>*Note: Throttle Max Range tests are calculated using PAS 1 with a rider weight of 165 lbs on flat terrain. Throttle speed and range may vary if ridden in different conditions.</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question-2": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<strong>Does Heybike Brawn Suitable for Riding on Beach?</strong>",
            "text": "<p>Brawn is an all-terrain ebike, built for adventure. Also suitable for riding on the beach, its fat tires ensure a smooth ride on the beach. However, please try to avoid seawater during the ride to prevent equipment damage.</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question-3": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<strong>Does Heybike Brawn Suitable For Heavey Riders?</strong>",
            "text": "<p>Sure, the max load capacity of Heybike Brawn is 400 lbs.</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question-4": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<strong>What Are The Benefits of Automatic Sensor Headlight on Heybike Brawn?</strong>",
            "text": "<p>They will automatically sense the surrounding environment and turn on sensitively in darker conditions. Improved visibility keeps you safe when riding at night or dark environment.</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question-5": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "<strong>What Are The Main Differences Between Heybike Brawn And Heybike Explore?</strong>",
            "text": "<p>Compared to Explore, Brawn upgraded many aspects to hydraulic system, such as hydraulic suspension front fork, hydraulic seat and hydraulic brake.</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        }
      },
